name: Alina Li
description:
Alina Li

She left us too soon...out of the industry into a life of food service thanks to poor treatment by bad people. However, you can still enjoy her perfection.

From a run of 5000 steps I pulled the 4000 step sample and think it's the most realistic.

Built on v1.5, as per usual she looks best on all of the nicer Models available here.

Do you like my work? Buy me a beer!
